  "description": "Melodica with sparse partials and maximum filter openness — the upper register where the plastic body resonance breaks up and each breath becomes visible. Almost a harmonica, almost a toy, completely unique. Play above C5 for the characteristic high-register breathiness. The instrument is at its most naked here.",
